  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Analysis of determinants and constraints of foreign investments to Tanzania</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Government of Tanzania have committed to increasing competitiveness to attract more investment, create jobs and boost productivity. Reforming the investment and business environment is increasingly a political priority with Senior Government figures referencing the importance in speeches but also actions such as the ratification of the African Continental Free Trade Agreement.
The objective of this assignment is to assess factors that either attract or impede foreign investment to Tanzania.</narrative>
  </description>
